dct_title_s: West Bank and east Jerusalem, population, January 1992.
dct_description_sm: Map shows estimated size and composition (Arab or Israeli) of villages and settlements. Includes notes on Israeli occupations and auxillary maps and diagrams showing proportional share of Arab and Jewish population. Also includes auxillary map: Jerusalem (1:75,000). Also shows Jerusalem city limit expansion. "725432 (540876) 6-92."
